Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:20.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:29.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:40.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:43.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:49.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:55.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:01:02.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:07.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:09.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:16.03,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:26.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:35.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:41.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:48.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:53.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:59.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:02.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:06.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:07.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:11.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:13.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:19.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:26.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:28.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:32.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:35.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:39.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:42.24,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bounty hunters have left\Nto hunt the Straw Hat Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who have fallen for their trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A total bounty of 600 million Berries, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see their Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we celebrate early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May our beloved Papa, Don Accino,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Accino Family's knit\Nblood relations be blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's to our present for Papa--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the heads of the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Dream Sinking in the New World!\NThe Disillusioned Pirate, Puzzle"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The icebergs moved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you morons?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for icebergs to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that's not quite what they meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't moving because of the currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're moving of their own accord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of their own accord?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't give us this crap\Nfirst thing in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For chunks of ice, they're bossy punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a mass of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it definitely moved to block our path...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iceberg itself seems normal enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were also those \NMarine ships last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like something is\Ntrying to lure us somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea who it is, \Nbut they've got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's duke it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first we have to figure out\Nwho exactly is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a great physician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not happy about getting called a\N"great physician" or anything, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro, what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were attacked by some really\Nstrong guys in the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is an attack like that even possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and carry the injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us out of here as fast as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still weren't ready... for the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like Puzzle the \NPhoenix to sound defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a whippersnapper \Nthat got in over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've followed you because we believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, I'll buy some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stansen, bring out the raiding dory!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the man who will\Nbecome the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Meteors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even First Officer Vigaro didn't last more\Nthan a few seconds up against them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But during that brief period of time,\Nhe managed to destroy their rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him, we were able to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone who\Nsurvived swore an oath!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be like our first officer\Nand protect the captain with our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be willing to lay down \Nmy life for Puzzle-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's protect the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Stansen-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think Vigaro was willing\Nto sacrifice his life to protect yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare throw your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're working for a group \Nof bounty hunters...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that they're incredibly strong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we were a mess after the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why we lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then they stole our Jolly Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our pride as the Phoenix Pirates....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stansen-san is a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all coming to an end today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle the Phoenix has risen once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel fine now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather the whole crew up on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain has regained consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we've been\Ndying for has finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the revival of the Phoenix Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that damn Stansen will\Nget what's coming to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, I'm sorry to have put you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagining today made it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san, I'm glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did what any doctor would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to pay you back someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we meet will\Nbe in the New World, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were also headed for \Nthe New World, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means we'll be\Nrivals from here on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we need to hop to \Nit and build up our forces
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can return to the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't going back to the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stansen's decision was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to continue working\Nfor those bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Have you lost your mind, Puzzle-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is willing to fight to\Nthe death, just like Vigaro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vigaro died... all for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the man who will\Nbecome the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have you on our side, Puzzle-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting this whole time\Nfor the Phoenix to rise from the ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Puzzle the Phoenix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Phoenix...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only existed\Nin the world of fairytales.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right to go to the New World\Nwhen I couldn't protect my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that, Captain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Jolly Roger \Nthey stole from us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a Jolly Roger anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost all sense of pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to thank you for tending to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm afraid we lost\Neverything in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those waters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World isn't as \Nforgiving as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find out when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find out when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take the New World lightly, Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Vigaro! I'm a phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's given up on their Jolly Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't pirates anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R... Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be fine without us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, take care of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to swerve around to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard a-starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard a-starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The icebergs are gathering together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're taking us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the waterways got blocked,\Nit created those whirlpools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with these waters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna turn that into\Nshaved ice and gobble it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaved ice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Devil Fruit power holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shaved ice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Arctic Path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any ship that wanders in never\Nsees the open ocean again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistaking him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Puzzle the Phoenix,\Nwith a bounty of 100 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he supposed to be dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been had!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Stansen guy tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy,\Na 300-million-Berry bounty, is with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bringing them to a total \Nof 400 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is turning into something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and inform Blend-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle the Phoenix is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare the fallen pirates \Ndeceive the Accino Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siblings, we can add another present\Nto the list for our beloved Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check on it right quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:18:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you take advantage of the \Nconfusion to grab onto Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you using the paddle wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fully charging the cola\Nbarrels in the energy room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my guess is right, there will definitely\Ncome a time when we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, if we're ever going\Nto get out of these crazy waters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...first we've got to unravel the\Npuzzle behind the moving icebergs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be some sort of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean squat to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a cinch for us \Nto get out of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dearies, now that you've\Nwandered into the Arctic Path,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never get to see\Nthe open ocean ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always see eye-to-eye, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That beautiful lady is \Nwith such a hideous man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you to a duel right here--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid we don't have \Ntime to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we took our leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just telling you \Nthat there is no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That expression was nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always see eye-to-eye, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What type of ship is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Salchow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is f-flying away in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you expect me to believe that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, he's telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is flying away\Nright before my very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, we've run into some trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not get the flag first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a splendid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to get the flag first, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, my honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lil-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you summon\Nthat one critter for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, um, I'm sorry, but you can't just--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lil-chan, you'd be doing it\Nas a favor for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it was an order from our beloved Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my kite, Uo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, we can finally relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean really is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue skies and white clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shining sun and the flapping Jolly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Jolly Roger is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Zoro appears to be missing, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they got lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are the icebergs \Ncold, but they keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the others are taking it easy,\Ndrinking tea on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that gaudy building?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Assassins Attack!\NThe Great Battle on Ice Begins"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
